These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, van, helicopter, trike, roller, boat
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, indian, mexican, russian, spanish
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the russian is between the person driving the boat and the american##2
5. the mexican is between the russian and the argentine##2
6. the american is the person driving the trike##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the american##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the person driving the van##1
9. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Transport           | bike | van | boat | roller | trike    | helicopter  |
| Nationality   | spanish | argentine   | mexican       | russian        | american | indian |

