.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bluemaster, havana, montecristo, game, prince
6 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig, horse, lizard, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the game-smoker##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the montecristo-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2
4. the havana-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
7. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | prince | game | montecristo | havana | pall-mall  |
| Pet           | snake | lizard  | frog | goat    | horse  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
House: art-deco, tower, gothic-revival, craftsman, cottage, victorian
The people use 6 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, taxi, tram, van
1. the art-deco house is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the craftsman house is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the cottage house##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
6. the cottage house is between the craftsman house and the person driving the helicopter##2
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the craftsman house##1
9. the tower house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| House         | tower | art-deco | victorian      | cottage | craftsman | gothic-revival      |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | van  | helicopter | taxi   | tram       | quad-bike |

