.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, vegafina, dannemann, swisher, bongani, oliveros
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the roller is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the fonseca-smoker is the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bike and the oliveros-smoker##2
7. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Cigar        | vegafina    | oliveros | dannemann | fonseca | bongani | swisher   |
| Transport   | scooter | taxi        | quad-bike  | bike     | trike  | roller |

