2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching sports movies##2
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
7. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | satire    | western | family | drama | sports   |
| Cigar         | baccarat | siglo | ritmeester | bluemaster | chaman  | tiparillo |

