.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, coffee, 7up, iced-tea, tea
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, reading, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking 7up and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
9. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Beverage    | water | tea | iced-tea  | 7up      | coffee | fanta  |
| Hobby   | card-games  | dancing    | reading | board-games | traveling | woodworking |

