.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: amber, blue, mauve, turquise, white, blood-red
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, roller, tram, van
1. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
3. the person who likes amber is between the person who likes white and the person who likes turquise##2
4. the person who likes turquise is the person driving the van##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
6. the person who likes white is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the tram##2
7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
8. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
9. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Color       | blood-red | turquise | amber | white | mauve | blue |
| Transport   | quad-bike | van    | tram  | bike    | roller    | boat    |

