1. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
3. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes amber and the person who likes blood-red##2
4. the musician is the person who likes azure##1
5. the mechanic is between the journalist and the social-worker##2
6. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
7. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
9. the mechanic is on the right of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Job           | musician | teacher | social-worker | mechanic | journalist | designer |
| Color   | azure   | black   | blue         | blood-red    | apricot     | amber     |

