.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: satire, action, western, animation, documentary, fantasy
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing, skateboarding, skiing, soccer, surfing
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
10. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | documentary  | action | animation | fantasy | western     |
| Sport   | sailing | biathlon | surfing    | soccer | skiing | skateboarding |

