.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, basketball, rugby, sailing, weightlifting
6 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the owner of the ferret is the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is rugby and the owner of the bird##2
9. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Sport   | basketball | weightlifting | rugby   | cycling | ice-hockey | sailing |
| Pet           | bird  | pony   | goldfish | ferret | snake       | rabbit |

