 3. the nurse is on the right of the accountant##1
 4. the nurse is on the far right##1
 5. the manager is between the chef and the owner of the frog##2
 6. the accountant is on the right of the teacher##1
 7. the teacher is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the teacher##1
 9. the owner of the cat is between the teacher and the owner of the chinchilla##2
10. the owner of the hedgehog is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | snake   | rabbit | frog       | hedgehog | cat    | chinchilla |
| Job   | chef | manager  | librarian | teacher      | accountant | nurse        |

