 3. the cain-smoker is the person watching scientific movies##1
 4. the havana-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the person watching time-travel movies##2
 5. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the bongani-smoker##2
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 7. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is the pall-mall-smoker##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Cigar           | cain      | davidoff | havana | pall-mall   | oliveros  | bongani |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy  | family             | time-travel | musical | sports       |

