4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is the bartender##1
6. the security-guard is between the journalist and the person who's birthday is in january##2
7. the person who's birthday is in july is between the pilot and the lawyer##2
