.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, collecting, cooking, drawing, rock-climbing, woodworking
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, oliveros, bolivar, blend, chaman, game
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the blend-smoker is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 6. the game-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the oliveros-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the bolivar-smoker is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is camping##2
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Hobby         | drawing | camping | collecting | woodworking | rock-climbing | cooking |
| Cigar   | baccarat | chaman | bolivar      | blend     | game       | oliveros |

 